
Changes
-calm <specific_npc>

Additions
valour <player>
  Cast a spell that lasts for about 10 min.  Every 10 seconds, it will
  give the player 1-3 hp for leading a fight.  Can only have one
  valour cast on one player.

undead_ward
  Create a ward of protection against low-level NPC spirits, demons etc.
  [It might kick necromancer pets right out of the room.  Boy I'm evil.]

spirit_armor
  Cast a spell to create a bonus against other|evil dmg and
  physical attacks by evil alignment attackers.

brotherhood
  All united knight brothers in combat receive a +1 wc while
  this spell lasts.



 
